txt.en: Do not change which sap you are covered with
Defeat no more than eighteen bog-lurkers ([placeholder]/18)
Disease has run rampant through the depths of Ost Dunhoth. Nature has been fouled by the poisoned waters. Once you have been marked with one of the diseases you must not change it.
The Huorns have fallen. Challenge complete.
The poisoned waters must gather into a stagnant pool at some point.
Once a Huorn has marked you with sap, do not replace it with the other Huorn's sap.
